test_list_of_single_number:
assert [[100], [100], [100]] == [[100]]
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: [100]
  Full diff:
  - [[100]]
  + [[100], [100], [100]]
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 100000000000 == 100
 +  where 100000000000 = <built-in function prod>([100, 1, 2, 4, 5, 10, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
